open source/how big the community


Flow executor
Requirements:
flow – is a sequence of tasks with a ability to execute next task based on the current task state
flow should be externally configurable (XML or JSON)
Task is a single unit of execution, works with one service only
Task can be sync or async
Should support sub-flows can be sync or async acts as a task for the parent flow
Parameters – ability to exchange data between tasks. Task can set parameters and read parameters. Task passes parameters to service methods
